properties.Name: ExperianConsumerAddress
properties.Description:
Addresses are listed on the credit report when they are reported to Experian by creditors. 

Any address that is reported as associated with an account may appear on the report.

Columns.Name: ExperianReportNumber
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of an Experian consumer.

Columns.Name: AddressId
Columns.Description: The address identification number is used to identify which accounts are associated with each individual address variation.

Columns.Name: ConsumerStreetPoBoxAddress
Columns.Description: The 'street/po box' component of the consumer address.

Columns.Name: ConsumerAddressCity
Columns.Description: The 'city' component of the consumer address.

Columns.Name: ConsumerAddressState
Columns.Description: The 'state' component of the consumer address.

Columns.Name: ConsumerAddressZipCode
Columns.Description: The 'zip code' component of the consumer address.

Columns.Name: ExperianResidenceTypeId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of an Experian residence type.

Columns.Name: ExperianGeographicalCode
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of an Experian Geographic location.
